Interface DvQuantified

All Superinterfaces:
org.openehr.base.foundation_types.Any, org.openehr.base.base_types.definitions.BasicDefinitions, DataValue, DvOrdered, org.openehr.base.base_types.definitions.OpenehrDefinitions, org.openehr.base.foundation_types.primitive_types.Ordered
All Known Subinterfaces:
DvAbsoluteQuantity, DvAmount, DvCount, DvDate, DvDateTime, DvDuration, DvProportion, DvQuantity, DvTemporal, DvTime
public interface DvQuantified extends DvOrdered
Abstract class defining the concept of true quantified values, i.e. values which are not only ordered, but which have a precise magnitude.
